Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.04,0:00:02.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.19,0:00:18.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade  In a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:42.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.82,0:00:48.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:52.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:57.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:00.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:07.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:11.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:17.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:19.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.30,0:01:30.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Aizen wasn’t enough for you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:35.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You even had to hurt\NHinamori this bad…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.31,0:01:43.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To make her grip her sword\Nso hard that her hands bled…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:58.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever made Hinamori bleed,\NI’d kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That will never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:15.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Draw your sword in a place like this…\Nand I’ll be forced to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:32.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Ichimaru…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Izuru…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t want to die yet,\Ndo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:44.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t be stupid.\NIt’s not enough just to stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:46.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, Kira…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my sight…\Nand even farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:56.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re within ten miles of me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:02.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t guarantee\NI won’t kill you by mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:29.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:44.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Toshiro Hitsugaya,\NCaptain of Squad 10…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:47.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A child prodigy of the sort\Nthat comes along
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,only once every few centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How very dangerous…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re serious, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:14.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Squad 10 Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like being cornered?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:05.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:11.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn’t have underestimated you…\NToshiro Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or I’ll end up\Nregretting it afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, not so fast…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because your true regret begins now…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:33.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You pushed me to it.\NRegret this in full!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.32,0:05:54.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reign over the Frosted Sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:15.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon of water and ice created\Nfrom overflowing Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…it can even control\Nthe weather…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I'm seeing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The most powerful zanpaku-to\Nof ice and snow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,wielded by Captain Hitsugaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:28.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hyorinmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So much water…! What speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:44.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t dodge it…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s over! Ichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:28.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pierce his flesh…Shinso!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:36.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure you wanna dodge this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:40.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll die…that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:41.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:50.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was returning to\Nmy quarters as ordered,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:02.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but I sensed Hyorinmaru’s\NSpiritual Pressure and came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please sheathe your sword,\NCaptain Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:13.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not…\NI shall engage you from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Day is breaking…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only two days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:51.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true that Ichigo is improving\Nwith startling speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Compared with that of\Nordinary Soul Reapers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,his growth is hard to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:09:00.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that only concerns\Nhis fighting skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His spiritual power\Nhas not risen as high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Warm-up exercises, finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:16.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where’d Yoruichi go, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get started soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can he achieve Bankai
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in only two days\Ngoing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should extend\Nthe deadline…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,According to the information\NI gathered,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,after Rukia had entered\Nthe Seireitei,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:40.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,her execution grace period was\Ncut five days short to 25 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:44.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So after Ichigo’s three days\Nof training,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:46.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the execution would’ve\Nbeen the following day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We had no time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:51.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But for good or bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:55.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when we came here, we were chased\Nby a Cleaner in the Senkaimon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:57.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and tore through\Nthe Dangai Precipice World.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:00.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That shifted the time axis\Nin our favor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when we fell into Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, even after\Nour three days of training,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we’ll still have eight more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.34,0:10:13.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It’s possible to extend\Nthe training!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But what do we do…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:22.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke developed that\Ntraining program based on himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:26.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only one ever to succeed\Nwas Kisuke himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, the 3-day period\Nis what it took
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:34.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for Kisuke to achieve Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And he determined that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:41.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a longer time period\Nwould be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He said…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:50.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kurosaki’s natural abilities\Nare greater than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I believed him and\Nbegan training Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there’s no guarantee that\NIchigo’s soul
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:02.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,can withstand\Nthe longer training period.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:04.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,HEY! Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?! Or are ya so scared\Nof me that you ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:15.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll wait one more day…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if there’s still no change\Nin his spiritual power,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:22.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just have to risk it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:32.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:48.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall repeat the notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your date of execution has been\Nchanged once more, Ms. Rukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:01.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution will\Ntake place tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:22.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn’t come,\NHinamori would’ve been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:25.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of coming after me…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look after the Lieutenant\Nof Squad 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He always disappears\Nwithout telling me where he’s going…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That still hasn’t changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:26.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gin… Where are you trying to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That letter of Aizen’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How much of it was forged?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:48.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Sokyoku\Nthat is going to be released
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at Rukia Kuchiki’s execution…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:01.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The plot to use that power\Nto destroy Soul Society…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:04.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was that line true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it is true…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:20.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s what Ichimaru\Nis after… I’ll…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hell Butterfly…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:28.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting to\Nthe Captains and Lieutenants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:30.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A change has been made
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:35.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,concerning the execution date\Nfor prisoner Rukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:39.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution will take place\N29 hours from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This ruling is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:47.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no further changes.\NThat is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution and\Nthe release of Sokyoku’s power…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:04.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If that’s Ichimaru’s aim,\NI can’t let this execution proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’re stopping the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To all Captains and Lieutenants,\Nreporting…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:23.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a final change in the execution date\Nof prisoner Rukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:28.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution will take\Nplace 29 hours from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:34.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat. There has been a final change\Nin the execution date
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,of prisoner Rukia Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.57,0:15:41.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution will take place\N29 hours from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This ruling is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:46.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no further changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no mistake.\NThat’s his Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be making\Nsteady progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:46.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But what’s this sense of\Nunease that I’m feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:53.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I sense something\Nominous approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what\Nyou were doing, holed up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s your zanpaku-to’s true form?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:18.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Secretly training for Bankai?\NThat looks like fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme train, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:27.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.47,0:17:33.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“What’re you doing here?”\NThat’s the look you’re giving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:40.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no special reason.\NWe’re outta time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:45.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I just wanted someplace\Nwhere I could concentrate on training.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:48.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Out of…time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:59.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, okay. I guess I'll tell you…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They changed Rukia’s\Ntime of execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:12.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The new time is noon tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:24.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it but my powers now\Nain’t good enough to save Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:32.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry. I ain’t gonna mess\Nwith your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:40.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve already mastered manifesting it.\NOnly a little more until Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:51.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just gonna do my own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tomorrow…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…he’ll never reach\NBankai by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:10.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just gonna quit,\NYoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:15.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren’t you the one\Nwho started me on this training?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then don’t be the first one\Nto give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:23.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichigo, if you can’t reach\NBankai by tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:24.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you…! Don’t talk about “can’t.”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:33.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If tomorrow’s the deadline…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:38.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll just finish it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His Spiritual Pressure…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This guy…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:12.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So tomorrow is the execution…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:17.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know… Before the execution, I’ll ask\Nthat Ichigo and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,be allowed to return\Nto the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:26.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to the Kuchiki clan, after all.\NThey might allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:32.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The execution is tomorrow…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:35.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard that,\NI was surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:38.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but strangely enough I wasn’t sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because of\Nthe dream I had last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:49.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That dream about the night\NI’ll never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:20:58.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:06.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:11.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:37.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:44.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody stand up! Everybody fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Within your heart, you may feel uneasy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:53.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But keep your head right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.35,0:21:55.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter when (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:21:59.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No matter where (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:02.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me anytime! (Oh yeah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be here for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:08.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:12.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With a tough smile
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.85,0:22:16.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.23,0:22:20.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s live!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:21.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:24.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people in the house
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happy people
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.81,0:22:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kaien…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.07,0:22:45.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of me…is worth saving…